                    <div class="container px-5 my-5">
                        <div class="row gx-5">
                            <div class="col-lg-4 mb-5 mb-lg-0">
                                <h2 class="fw-bolder mb-0">You can book G2/G drive
                                    test from this kiosk.</h2>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-lg-8">
                                <div class="row gx-5 row-cols-1 row-cols-md-2">
                                    <div class="col mb-5 h-100">
                                        <div class="feature bg-primary bg-gradient text-white rounded-3 mb-3"><i
                                                class="bi bi-collection"></i></div>
                                        <h2 class="h5">Conquer Your Driving Test
                                            with Confidence</h2>
                                        <p class="mb-0">Feeling nervous about your
                                            upcoming driving test? We've got you
                                            covered! <span class="cname">DriveTest</span>
                                            offers everything you need to
                                            ace your test, from practice tests and
                                            road sign guides to expert tips and
                                            calming techniques.</p>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="col mb-5 h-100">
                                        <div class="feature bg-primary bg-gradient text-white rounded-3 mb-3"><i
                                                class="bi bi-building"></i></div>
                                        <h2 class="h5">Pass Your G2/G Test on the
                                            First Try</h2>
                                        <p class="mb-0">Don't waste time and money
                                            on retakes. Our comprehensive study
                                            materials and practice tests ensure
                                            you're fully prepared for your G2 or G
                                            test. Increase your chances of success
                                            and get your license faster.</p>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="col mb-5 mb-md-0 h-100">
                                        <div class="feature bg-primary bg-gradient text-white rounded-3 mb-3"><i
                                                class="bi bi-toggles2"></i></div>
                                        <h2 class="h5">Brush Up Your Skills for a
                                            Smooth Renewal</h2>
                                        <p class="mb-0">Haven't driven in a while or
                                            need a refresher on the rules of
                                            the road? <span class="cname">DriveTest</span> can
                                            help! Our resources are
                                            perfect for experienced drivers looking
                                            to boost their knowledge and
                                            confidence before their license renewal
                                            test.</p>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="col h-100">
                                        <div class="feature bg-primary bg-gradient text-white rounded-3 mb-3"><i
                                                class="bi bi-toggles2"></i></div>
                                        <h2 class="h5">Get Your Learner's Permit
                                            Quickly and Easily</h2>
                                        <p class="mb-0">Eager to hit the road and
                                            start your driving journey? We can
                                            help you get there! Our study guides and
                                            practice permit tests will prepare
                                            you for the written test and give you a
                                            head start on your driving lessons.
                                        </p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </section>
                <!-- Testimonial section-->
                <div class="py-5 bg-light">
                    <div class="container px-5 my-5">
                        <div class="row gx-5 justify-content-center">
                            <div class="col-lg-10 col-xl-7">
                                <div class="text-center">
